      "id": "candidate-parameterized-art-generation",
      "canonical_name": "Parameterized Art Generation",
      "zh_name": "参数化艺术生成",
      "category": "tool",
      "status": "candidate",
      "definition": {
        "zh": "通过参数化代码模板和外部渲染库，将用户意图转化为生成艺术作品的技能模式。",
        "en": "A skill pattern that transforms user intent into generative art artifacts using parameterized code templates and external rendering libraries."
      },
      "problem": {
        "zh": "用户想要创建算法艺术，但缺乏将创意意图转化为可执行代码的方法，且需面对复杂的渲染库。",
        "en": "Users want to create algorithmic art but lack a method to translate creative intent into executable code while facing complex rendering libraries."
      },
      "solution": {
        "zh": "提供预置模板和参数接口，指导模型填充关键变量并调用外部库（如p5.js），输出可直接运行的艺术代码或可视化结果。",
        "en": "Provide preset templates and parameter interfaces, instructing the model to fill key variables and call external libraries (e.g., p5.js), outputting directly runnable art code or visual results."
      },
      "when_to_use": {
        "zh": "当任务涉及创意编程或生成性视觉输出，且存在可复用的代码模板时。",
        "en": "When the task involves creative coding or generative visual output and there is a reusable code template."
      },
